{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I must have been fairly good at picking up languages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the other hand, I've recently discovered that I never learned the bases of any language.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've picked up all languages on the basis of listening to other people and imitating them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that way, maybe I am fortunate in not having too many accents in most of the languages I can now speak.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've never really learned the grammar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in writing my book, I find this a quite a handicap, actually, that I never really quite know how to write certain things the proper way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Holland was probably the best years of my life, or of my childhood, certainly, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We, we soon made lots of friends in the street and also at school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in those days, apart from school, which I used to enjoy very much like all the other schools before-- but there, I really got down to the sports business, which maybe I'd learned from Rudi.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But Holland, of course, was an ideal place for swimming, first of all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody went swimming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you had to have certificates and diplomas in order to be allowed to go into the deep end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you had to pass these examinations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you had to swim-- be able to swim with all your clothes on, and all those kind of things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember all that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I have the certificates here to show you that I passed them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you had to have cycling-- cycling was another big thing Holland, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We all had bicycles, even father, mother, Ruti.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We all had a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you had to pass tests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you got a certificate that you were-- proficiency type of-- proficient in, in riding bicycles kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
